      <title>保守党候选人：领导英国反对党的六位候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/conservative-party-runners-and-riders-the-six-candidates-to-lead-uk-opposition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[六名国会议员将角逐前首相里希·苏纳克（Rishi Sunak）的英国保守党领袖一职，并肩负起让保守党从史上最惨痛选举失败中重生的任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/conservative-party-runners-and-riders-the-six-candidates-to-lead-uk-opposition</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 13:37:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
